<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Your Website - Home</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styles here */

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Change font family to Arial */
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); /* Light black background */
            color: #fff; /* White text color */
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #333; /* Dark header color */
        }

        .latest-news {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .latest-news h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the text bold */
        }

        .news-list {
            flex: 0.5;
        }

        .news-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .news-item img {
            max-width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .news-item h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the text bold */
        }

        .news-content p {
            display: none;
        }

        .side-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Align content horizontally to the center */
            align-items: center; /* Align content vertically to the center */
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack elements vertically */
            max-width: 70%;
        }

        .side-content img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .side-content p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ccc; /* Light grey text color */
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the text bold */
        }

        .search {
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        /* Highlight active nav link */
        .navbar-nav .nav-item.active .nav-link {
            color: #fff;
            
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item .nav-link {
            color: #ccc; /* Grey color for nav links */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="t1">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">News Channel</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
            aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
            <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/news">News</a>
                </li>
                
                
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <form class="form-inline my-2 my-lg-0" action="/search" method="GET">
                <input class="form-control mr-sm-2" type="text" name="query" placeholder="Search news..."
                    aria-label="Search">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-success my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit">Search</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="home">
        <div class="latest-news">
            <div class="news-list">
                <h2>Latest News</h2>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <% newsList.forEach(news => { %>
                    <li class="news-item">
                        <!-- Link to the individual news article page -->
                        <a href="/news/<%= news.id %>" class="text-decoration-none">
                            <% if (news.imageUrl) { %>
                            <img src="<%= news.imageUrl %>" alt="News Image" class="img-fluid">
                            <% } %>
                            <div class="news-content">
                                <h3><%= news.title %></h3>
                                <p><%= news.content %></p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <% }); %>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="side-content">

                <img src="https://www.anits.edu.in/images/banner4.jpg" alt="teju" class="img-fluid">

                <p>Anil Neerukonda Institute of Technology and Sciences (ANITS) is a renowned engineering college located
                    in Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India. It was established in the year 2001 and is named after the
                    famous industrialist and philanthropist, Late Sri Anil Neerukonda. ANITS is affiliated with Andhra
                    University and is approved by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi.

                    The college offers undergraduate and postgraduate programs in various disciplines of engineering,
                    including Computer Science, Electronics and Communication, Mechanical, Civil, and Electrical
                    Engineering. ANITS is known for its excellent academic standards, state-of-the-art infrastructure,
                    and experienced faculty members. The college also emphasizes research and innovation, encouraging
                    students to participate in various projects and competitions.

                    ANITS has a vibrant campus life with numerous extracurricular activities, clubs, and events that
                    help in the overall development of students. The college has a strong placement record, with many
                    students securing placements in reputed companies every year. ANITS is considered one of the top
                    engineering colleges in Andhra Pradesh and is a preferred choice for students seeking quality
                    technical education.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div> 

    <!-- Bootstrap JS (Optional) -->
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>